You remain in complete control throughout this experience.<break time="2s"/>
At any time,<break time="1s"/> you can return to full waking awareness simply by opening your eyes.<break time="2.5s"/>
You are safe,<break time="1.5s"/> supported,<break time="1.5s"/> and held in sacred space.<break time="3s"/>

Find a comfortable position now,<break time="2s"/> where your body can fully relax.<break time="2s"/>
Perhaps sitting with your spine gently supported,<break time="1.5s"/> or lying down with your arms at your sides.<break time="2.5s"/>
