This time is yours,<break time="1.5s"/> a sacred offering to your own inner light.<break time="3s"/>

Allow your eyes to close when you feel ready,<break time="2s"/> and know that whatever insights come,<break time="1.5s"/> whatever images arise,<break time="1.5s"/> they come in service of your highest good.<break time="3.5s"/>

