</prosody>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: MAIN JOURNEY -->
<!-- Duration: 14 minutes | Pitch: -1st | Purpose: Dance with Amaterasu -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="-1st">
You pass beneath the torii,<break time="2.5s"/> and with each step along the white stone path,<break time="2.5s"/> the light around you begins to change.<break time="3.5s"/>

The sky above shifts from deep indigo,<break time="2s"/> to violet,<break time="2s"/> to the softest rose,<break time="2.5s"/> as though the world itself is awakening.<break time="4s"/>

You climb higher,<break time="2s"/> and the mist parts gently before you,<break time="2.5s"/> revealing the temple ahead,<break time="2s"/> its curved roof gleaming with golden tiles,<break time="2.5s"/> its wooden beams carved with sacred symbols.<break time="4s"/>

