The space is vast,<break time="2s"/> yet intimate,<break time="2s"/> lit by paper lanterns that glow like small moons.<break time="3.5s"/>
The scent of sandalwood and jasmine fills the air,<break time="2.5s"/> and beneath your feet,<break time="2s"/> smooth wooden floors shine with a deep luster.<break time="4s"/>

At the center of the temple,<break time="2.5s"/> you see an opening,<break time="2s"/> a circular well of light,<break time="2.5s"/> where the roof draws back to reveal the sky.<break time="4s"/>

And there,<break time="2s"/> descending through that opening,<break time="2.5s"/> comes a presence of pure radiance.<break time="4.5s"/>

Amaterasu,<break time="2s"/> the Great Goddess of the Sun,<break time="2.5s"/> arrives.<break time="4s"/>

