She does not speak,<break time="2s"/> but you hear her,<break time="2.5s"/> within.<break time="3s"/>

<emphasis level="strong">Welcome, beloved one.</emphasis><break time="3s"/>
<emphasis level="strong">You have traveled far to meet me here.</emphasis><break time="4s"/>

