<emphasis level="moderate">It is time to remember your own radiance.</emphasis><break time="4s"/>

Amaterasu extends her hand toward you,<break time="2.5s"/> and in her palm,<break time="2s"/> a sphere of golden light appears,<break time="2.5s"/> pulsing gently,<break time="2s"/> like a living heart.<break time="4s"/>

<emphasis level="strong">This is the light you have forgotten,</emphasis><break time="2.5s"/> she says,<break time="2s"/> <emphasis level="strong">the brilliance you were born to carry.</emphasis><break time="4.5s"/>

She steps closer,<break time="2.5s"/> and brings the sphere to your chest,<break time="2.5s"/> pressing it gently into your heart space.<break time="4s"/>

And as it enters,<break time="2.5s"/> you feel warmth flooding through you,<break time="2.5s"/> spreading out in waves,<break time="2s"/> golden and alive.<break time="4.5s"/>

Your body begins to glow,<break time="2.5s"/> softly at first,<break time="2s"/> then brighter,<break time="2.5s"/> as though you have swallowed the sun itself.<break time="4.5s"/>

And now,<break time="2s"/> Amaterasu takes both your hands,<break time="2.5s"/> and she begins to move,<break time="2s"/> slowly,<break time="2s"/> gracefully,<break time="2.5s"/> inviting you into a dance.<break time="4.5s"/>

